statements.name: PROC PRTEXP
statements.description: Replicates, modifies, and creates printer definitions.

arguments.name: USESASHELP
arguments.description: specifies that SAS search only the SASHELP portion of the registry for printer definitions.

arguments.name: OUT=
arguments.description: specifies the SAS data set that contains the printer definitions.

statements.name: EXCLUDE
statements.description: Names the printers whose information does not appear in output.

arguments.name: printer
arguments.description: specifies one or more printers that you do not want the output to contain information about.

statements.name: SELECT
statements.description: Names the printers whose information is contained in the output.

arguments.name: printer
arguments.description: specifies one or more printers that you would like the output to contain information about.
